OL,4,CCovid: Isolation rules loosened for
OL,5,Ccritical workers
OL,6, Some fully vaccinated people in
OL,7, critical roles, including NHS and care
OL,8, staff, will be able to continue working
OL,9, even if they are told to self-isolate.
OL,11,FMinister Nadhim Zahawi said isolation
OL,12,Frules for close contacts in England
OL,13,Fwould change shortly to allow those
OL,14,Feligible to take daily tests instead.
OL,16,FThe new rule was announced as most
OL,17,Fremaining curbs in England ended on
OL,18,FMonday, including face mask laws.
OL,20,FIt follows mounting criticism of the
OL,21,Fimpact of self-isolation on industry.
